Package: fcnet
Title: Functional Connectivity Analysis Tools for fMRI Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Shijing", "Zhou", , "shijingz@uoregon.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7053-0953"))
Description: Tools for analyzing network-level functional connectivity from 
    fMRI data using parcellated brain atlases. Extracts network and ROI 
    groupings, calculates within-network, between-network, and user-defined 
    connectivity metrics, and generates visualizations. Supports loading 
    connectivity matrices from the CONN toolbox, flexible ROI definitions, 
    and custom network assignments. Designed for the Schaefer atlas but 
    adaptable to other parcellation schemes.
